- [ ] decode_port_message correctly decodes {Port, {data, Binary}}
- [ ] decode_port_message correctly decodes {Port, {exit_status, Code}}
- [ ] Returns Error(Nil) for non-matching port
- [ ] Returns Error(Nil) for unknown message shapes
- [ ] All tests pass

